name: Clairvoyant
description: Druids tried for centuries to read animal behavior to divine the future, with scarce results. Tired, some turned into Haruspices and focused on dissecting the animals, exposing and reading their guts. But some weren't quite satisfied, and evolved to turn humans inside out just to get a glimpse of their own future. These are called Clairvoyants. Made by @Flygohr
